headline: Valtech Expands Americas Leadership to Drive AI-Powered Capabilities and Expand New Business
summary: Valtech announces significant leadership appointments to fast-track innovation and value in the Americas. Adam Hasemeyer is being promoted to CEO of the Americas. He'll be joined by new hires Nischal Kapoor, EVP Growth – Enterprise Transformation, formerly from Accenture, and Nathan Oliver, EVP Head of Business Development, from Plus Company.
